# Base URL for the rfc-api backend.
#
# - Local dev (per docs/integration/rfc-api-reference.md#local-development):
#     RFC_API_URL=http://localhost:8080
# - Container / k8s deployments: set to the cluster-internal service URL.
#
# Vite only exposes vars prefixed with VITE_ to the client by default.
# `src/portal/api/config.ts` reads the unprefixed form first so SSR /
# Node entry points pick it up via process.env, then falls back to
# VITE_RFC_API_URL for client-side.
RFC_API_URL=http://localhost:8080
